 Dare Adeboye General Overseer of Redeemed Christian Church of God, RCCG Enoch Adejare Adeboye has lost his son, Pastor Dare Adeboye to the cold hands of death. According to reports, Pastor Dare, 42 died in his sleep on Wednesday in Eket, Akwa Ibom State, where he was staying with his family. It was gathered that the Assistant Pastor in Charge of Region (Youth) 35, had ministered the previous day. According to the wife of the deceased, Temiloluwa Adeboye, she realized her husband’s unusual sleeping hours and couldn’t get him on phone. She allegedly alerted her neighbours and he was found dead. It was said that the deceased was neither ill nor on medication before the unexpected happened. A source said; “He was not sick and did not complain of anything before the incident. Pastors in the church were summoned to pray for him, all to no avail,”